headline: Spire to Report Q1 Earnings: What's in Store for the Stock?
summary: SR is likely to report Q1 earnings results on Feb. 3, with new rates, lower interest costs and storage expansion in focus, even as higher O&M expenses loom.

headline: Is Pinnacle West Capital (PNW) Fairly Priced After Recent Share Price Gains?
summary: Wondering if Pinnacle West Capital at around US$93.68 is offering fair value right now, or if the price is getting ahead of itself? This article is built to help you answer that. The stock has returned 0.2% over the last week, 5.4% over the last month, 6.3% year to date, 13.5% over 1 year, 37.8% over 3 years and 50.8% over 5 years.
